<h2>Brew-php</h2>
some php related formulas

<h3>Requirements</h3>
<ul>
<li>Homebrew</li>
<li>Snow Leopard - Lion</li>
</ul>

<h3>Description</h3>
[xhprof]
brew php xhprof
A Hierarchical Profiler for PHP

install:
1-download xhprof.rb
2-<pre><code>mv xhprof.rb `brew --prefix`/Library/Formula</code></pre>
3-<pre><code>brew install xhprof</code></pre>

Doc:
http://pecl.php.net/package/xhprof


[http-php]
brew php http
Extended HTTP Support

install:
1-download http-php.rb
2-<pre><code>mv http-php.rb `brew --prefix`/Library/Formula</code></pre>
3-<pre><code>brew install http-php</code></pre>

Doc:
http://php.net/manual/en/book.http.php


[ssh-php]
brew php ssh2
Bindings for the libssh2 library

install:
1-download ssh-php.rb
2-<pre><code>mv ssh-php.rb `brew --prefix`/Library/Formula</code></pre>
3-<pre><code>brew install ssh-php</code></pre>

Doc:
http://pecl.php.net/package/ssh2